(I. INTRODUCTION) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(As a key technology of this convergence, edge intelligence pushes model) Tj
T*
(training and inference from centralized datacenters toward the places where) Tj
T*
(data originates. Surveys of mobile edge computing chart the communication) Tj
T*
(perspective of this shift, while landmark deep learning results motivate the) Tj
T*
(demand for computation everywhere. Federated optimization demonstrates that) Tj
T*
(learning can proceed without centralizing raw data, and efficient) Tj
T*
(architectures bring inference to resource-constrained devices. Standards) Tj
T*
(bodies meanwhile define reference architectures for multi-access edge) Tj
T*
(computing. The remainder of this document exists solely to carry the) Tj
T*
(reference list on the following pages.) Tj
